### Seed demo vehicles
POST http://localhost:8080/api/local/seed

###

### Get demo customer (grab the id for use below)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/local/me

###

### Browse all available vehicles
GET http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles

###

### Browse by city
GET http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles?city=Amsterdam

###

### Browse by class (CITY_SMALL, LONG_RANGE, FUN_PREMIUM, BULKY)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles?vehicleClass=CITY_SMALL

###

### Get a specific vehicle
GET http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles/{{vehicleId}}

###

### View damage reports for a vehicle
GET http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles/{{vehicleId}}/damage-reports

###

### Report new damage
POST http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles/{{vehicleId}}/damage-reports
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "position": "FRONT",
  "photoUrl": "https://example.com/photo.jpg",
  "licensePlatePhotoUrl": "https://example.com/plate.jpg",
  "notes": "Small scratch on bumper"
}

###

### Reserve a vehicle
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations?vehicleId={{vehicleId}}

###

### Extend a reservation by 10 minutes
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/{{reservationId}}/extend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "additionalMinutes": 10
}

###

### Cancel a reservation
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/{{reservationId}}

###

### Start a rental
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rentals/start?reservationId={{reservationId}}

###

### Get active rental
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rentals/active

###

### End a rental (triggers invoice + Stripe charge)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rentals/{{rentalId}}/end

###

### Start KYC verification (returns a Veriff URL)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/customers/me/kyc/start

###

### Add a payment method
POST http://localhost:8080/api/customers/me/payment-method
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentMethodId": "pm_card_visa"
}
